---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Science — Evergreen Assessments" description="Validated psychometrics, transparent practices, and fairness by design.">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Science</h1>
    <section class="mt-4 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-medium">Validation philosophy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">We prioritize construct clarity, reliability, criterion validity, and longitudinal sensitivity. Methods include classical test theory and IRT as appropriate, with transparent reporting.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-medium">Fairness & bias monitoring</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">We evaluate differential item functioning and adverse impact, and monitor model‑mediated dialogue for biased suggestions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-medium">Privacy & data minimization</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">Only essential data are collected for scoring and feedback. De‑identification and aggregation are standard for research metrics.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-medium">Transparent roadmap</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">Planned disclosures include measurement invariance studies, technical manuals, and release notes for any model changes affecting scores.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
